utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_01
utterances.text: You're ready? You feel ready?

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: Yes.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_01
utterances.text: I don't know what caused you to volunteer, why you're here, but I'd be glad to hear whatever's on your mind.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: I was invited to volunteer and I happily accepted.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: I want to do this and it was an opportunity presented to me so I'm here.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_01
utterances.text: Okay.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: And I'm feeling quite frightened.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: And I have not picked out for myself any agenda right now.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: I can talk a little bit about what's going on in my life, which is my ongoing agenda, I suppose.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_01
utterances.text: The immediate agenda is that it's kind of scary.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: Yes, and I feel really very exposed and self-conscious.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: But I also feel that some part of me is delighted to be sitting here in front of you and talking to you.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: I'm a little distracted by some noises behind me, a rumbling, I don't know what that is.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_01
utterances.text: I think that's outside.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_01
utterances.text: I don't...

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_01
utterances.text: Anyway, let's try and disregard that.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: Okay.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: I feel not quite as anxious now as I did a moment ago.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: So the most obvious thing for me to talk about is the fact that I'm going through a divorce.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: Papers were filed in spring and the divorce should be final in fall.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: There's lots of material there, which is very close to the surface for me.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: I am in a small group which I value very highly.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: It's been very good for me.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: And two days ago I did a lot of intense work in that small group.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: I ventilated a lot of pain and talked about what's going on with me and got some excellent support from my group.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: Right now I'm feeling a little strange about repeating what I just said at that time.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_01
utterances.text: I don't quite know whether that's the place to start or not, but at least that was helpful to you again.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: Yes.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_01
utterances.text: Really got some things out.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: Yes.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: I'm feeling sad that the workshop is going to end in about 24 hours.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: I feel with respect to many people here both a strong connection and some pain that I haven't spent more time with various individuals, ambivalence.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: And now I'm feeling awkward because I feel as though it's my task to produce something to talk about, and I'm not quite sure what to do with that, and I'm afraid of making a decision which will feel artificial.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: And so I'm feeling,

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: Part of me wants to be passive and wait for something to be suggested to me.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_01
utterances.text: It is kind of a tough spot because you don't want to produce a problem.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_01
utterances.text: If there is anything you want to talk about, you want it to be real.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: Mm-hmm, that's right.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: I was immediately, as you said that, I thought of some things that I was feeling as I heard you talking in the first hour, hour and a half.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: And I was moved by several of the things that you said and the reports you gave.

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: And it comes from a place in me which just very passionately and deeply wants connection,

utterances.speaker: SPEAKER_00
utterances.text: harmony, peace.
